== Death ==
Markus Mayer died in 2025 in his hometown Salzburg at the age of 36 due to Hepatitis B. He lost his long fight against this horrible disease. He got it when he was young after clubbing. He left his 4 children, little sister Bettina and beloved wife Halimnye. Rest in peace, Legend! 🕊
